    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "The user runs several distinct Claude implementations",
      "uuid": "a74fbf6b11b241849a962450bdaa4caa",
      "x": -1704.340177205188,
      "y": 1515.064408618291,
      "width": 545.0,
      "height": 131.0,
      "z_value": -9.92700000000004,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "  And by deliberate naming convention they are (almost) all just called \"Claude\" \u2014 so terminology collisions are routine, not sloppiness. When a request names \"Claude\", \"the proofreader\", \"ClaudeNode\", etc., and more than one could fit, confirm WHICH one is meant before acting."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "image",
      "title": "Image",
      "uuid": "b6b8c9d957eb496e99be3fa08a9310b7",
      "x": 2625.1176470588234,
      "y": -604.9166232523088,
      "width": 359.2236300292325,
      "height": 378.06769244526095,
      "z_value": 0.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": false,
      "image_b64": "",
      "cache_key": "c98e350354139cab6f92cfe689df4f160d2c40cbe3b6dc46fa0591dde6f5c5d4",
      "caption": "Two abstract human figures light",
      "source_path": "C:\\Users\\thisg\\Desktop\\A Charm in the shape of an Expressed Emotion\\Images\\downloadedImage (7).png",
      "source_size": 1071160,
      "source_mtime": 1771066639.4457555,
      "show_border": true,
      "depth_front": false
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "7fdec9139eb64df2ac93708b0e6e7c23",
      "x": -999999.0,
      "y": -999999.0,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 204.0,
      "z_value": 0.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "`int()` first, then `// 2`, plus a `max(1, ...)` guard so it can't be zero on a degenerate node. The spiral search will now run correctly.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "That's not a node editor.  That is a new medium",
      "uuid": "178a80cd90644c24b3d00c2f7afa8ce1",
      "x": -1025.4099562839324,
      "y": 49.96339647876454,
      "width": 501.0545528166878,
